        <source>openShipDelayEnquiryForm(_voyage : CM_Voyage ; _voyageColl : CM_VoyageSet) protected;
/*
----------   ----------  --------------------------------------------------
Created:	14 February 2007 By cnwmo1

Purpose:	

Changed On   Changed By  Reason
	
----------   ----------  --------------------------------------------------
02/04/2010	cnwcs5	Moved delays forms up to UiCommonSchema
